Let's convert it to a data frame so we can manipulate it more easily. We can do this with the `tibble` function.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
orf_df <- tibble(
  name = names(orfs),
  orf_start = start(orfs),
  orf_end = end(orfs),
  orf_width = width(orfs)
)

gt(orf_df)
```

