We can also make a new FASTA file containing only the sequences for your identified ERV ORFs.

First, we get only the ORF name column from our identified ERV ORF table.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
name_col <- identified_orf_df |>
  pull(name)

print(name_col)
```

