We can then use this variable to subset our ORF amino acid sequences, which stored earlier in our `AAStringSet` object named `orf_aa_seqs`.



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
identified_orf_seqs <- orf_aa_seqs[name_col]
```
